<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Description">Description</span></h2>
<pre><b>meta_data = resource_info(filename)</b>
</pre>
<p><b>resource_info</b> can be used to get information of a resource file. This can also be used to check if a resource exists.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Return_value">Return value</span></h2>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr>
<th>Argument</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Description
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td><b>meta_data</b></td>
<td><i>Table</i></td>
<td>This object contains all the information of the queried resource. Note that this value is nil when the resource does not exist.
</td></tr></tbody></table>
